<p>I did a small "Last Changes" recursive loop in my template. Problem is how do i get to display only the first 10 or so? The cnt variable gets reset on every loop.</p>  <pre><code>&lt;div id="latest"&gt;     &lt;h4&gt;Last Changes&lt;/h4&gt;      {% macro loop(page, cnt) %}          {% for p in page.children.visible  %}             {% if p.template == 'docs' %}                 {% set cnt = cnt + 1 %}                   &lt;li class="recent-posts"&gt;                     &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="{{ p.url }}"&gt;{{ p.menu }} - {{cnt}}&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;                     {% if p.children.count &gt; 0 %}                         {{ _self.loop(p, cnt) }}                     {% endif %}                 &lt;/li&gt;              {% endif %}         {% endfor %}     {% endmacro %}      &lt;ul&gt;         {% for page in pages.children.order('modified', 'desc') %}            {{ _self.loop(page, 0) }}         {% endfor %}     &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;/div&gt; </code></pre>